OL,3,C'I'm going, I'm going': Man in cardiac
OL,4,Carrest while on phone to 999
OL,6,FA Castleford man who went into cardiac
OL,7,Farrest while on the phone to 999 has
OL,8,Fbeen teaching students CPR.
OL,10,FMark Spedding, an ambulance care
OL,11,Fassistant, called for help while going
OL,12,Finto cardiac arrest when he was home
OL,13,Falone in Normanton.
OL,15,FWhen a Yorkshire Ambulance Service
OL,16,Fworker picked up, they asked whether
OL,17,Fthe patient was breathing.
OL,19,FIn response, Mr Spedding, 59, said:
OL,20,F"Only just, love. I'm on me own. I
OL,21,Fthink I'm having a heart attack.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
