OL,3,C'I'm going, I'm going': Man in cardiac
OL,4,Carrest while on phone to 999
OL,6,F"I think I'm going, love. I'm going.
OL,7,FI'm going."
OL,9,FThe father-of-three was on call for
OL,10,Fabout a minute and managed to give his
OL,11,Fname, address and symptoms to the call
OL,12,Fhandler before he became unconscious.
OL,14,FAmbulance workers, who were in fact Mr
OL,15,FSpedding's colleagues, managed to
OL,16,Fresuscitate him and he was taken to
OL,17,Fhospital for further treatment.
OL,19,FHe spent two days in an induced coma
OL,20,Fand was discharged two weeks later.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
