OL,3,C'I'm going, I'm going': Man in cardiac
OL,4,Carrest while on phone to 999
OL,6,FMr Spedding has been sharing his
OL,7,Fexperiences about the importance of
OL,8,FCPR with students at Penistone Grammar
OL,9,FSchool for Restart a Heart Day.
OL,11,FTo mark the day, Yorkshire Ambulance
OL,12,FService visited 172 schools across the
OL,13,Fregion to provide CPR training to more
OL,14,Fthan 35,000 students on Wednesday, 16
OL,15,FOctober.
OL,17,FOne student being taught said: "I
OL,18,Fthink I would know what to do but I
OL,19,Fwould be really nervous. I think this
OL,20,Fdefinitely helped in confidence."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
