OL,3,C'I'm going, I'm going': Man in cardiac
OL,4,Carrest while on phone to 999
OL,6,FAnother student said: "It could happen
OL,7,Fto anyone at any time so it's
OL,8,Fimportant to know how to do it."
OL,10,FAssociate Vice Principal Katie Crook
OL,11,Fsaid: "Maths, English, core subjects,
OL,12,Fof course we are here to educate and
OL,13,Fthey are super important. But having
OL,14,Fthat skill and understanding to help
OL,15,Fsomebody is just fabulous so we are
OL,16,Freally proud to do that here at
OL,17,FPenistone."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
