OL,3,C'I'm going, I'm going': Man in cardiac
OL,4,Carrest while on phone to 999
OL,6,F"We know about three students who took
OL,7,Fpart in Restart a Hear Day last year
OL,8,Fwho have since used CPR to help save
OL,9,Fthe lives of parents which is
OL,10,Fincredible and really emphasises the
OL,11,Fimportant of our campaign and knowing
OL,12,Fwhat to do."
OL,14,FCurrently in the UK, less than one in
OL,15,Ften people survive and out-of-hospital
OL,16,Fcardiac arrest.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
