OL,3,C'I'm going, I'm going': Man in cardiac
OL,4,Carrest while on phone to 999
OL,6,FMr Carlyon said: "If we achieved the
OL,7,Fsame survival rates of countries like
OL,8,FNorway, where CPR is taught in
OL,9,Fschools, an additional 100 lives could
OL,10,Fbe saved each week - the equivalent of
OL,11,Fapproximately 5,000 every year."
OL,13,FIn August 2024, Mark, who has worked
OL,14,Ffor the ambulance service for 6 years,
OL,15,Fwas reunited with the colleagues who
OL,16,Fsaved his life.
OL,18,FHe said: "It was very emotional, but
OL,19,Fin a good way. How do you thank the
OL,20,Fpeople who have saved your life? No
OL,21,Fwords could ever do it justice.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
