OL,3,C'I'm going, I'm going': Man in cardiac
OL,4,Carrest while on phone to 999
OL,6,F"We are all human at the end of the
OL,7,Fday and regardless of the job we do,
OL,8,Fworking to resuscitate someone you
OL,9,Fknow is difficult, but they put that
OL,10,Faside and the exceptional care they
OL,11,Fdelivered was just fantastic. I
OL,12,Fwouldn't be here without them."
OL,14,FArea Operations Manager with Yorkshire
OL,15,FAmbulance Service, Dwain Longley,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Ambulance crews attend patients
OL,17,Fwho are critically unwell every day
OL,18,Fand while they are highly trained,
OL,19,Fthis still offers its own challenges
OL,20,Fand difficulties.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
