OL,3,C'I'm going, I'm going': Man in cardiac
OL,4,Carrest while on phone to 999
OL,6,F"But to attend someone who you know
OL,7,Fpersonally and have worked wiath
OL,8,Foperationally adds its own dynamic. To
OL,9,Fbe able to resuscitate them is an
OL,10,Fachievement but to be able to meet
OL,11,Fthat individual afterwards and see
OL,12,Fthey have not suffered any lasting
OL,13,Fdetrimental effect is truly an honour
OL,14,Ffor both the crews and patient."
